        jLabel23.setText("<html><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> WAY TO GO SHOPPERS! This is a place that you will surely love. Knowing that this mall is the biggest in Asia. Yep! you read it right. Not just in the Philippines but in the whole continent of Asia.  This is totally the most amazing place to visit in Manila. Food Chains and restaurants here offer the best foods in town. And because it is the biggest mall in Asia, many artist have their concerts here. Recently, The Vamps, Justin Bieber, Bruno Mars and many more. ");
